<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional //EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html charset=UTF-8" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="body">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
          <img
            src="https://www.yourbuzzz.com/images/logo-with-text.png"
            alt="Logo"
            title="Logo"
            style="display: inline"
            width="100%"
            height="60"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="contents">
          <p>Dear {{name}},</p>

          <p>
            I hope this message finds you well. We're ready to deliver your
            Buzzz order but we've noticed your phone number is missing. This is
            essential for coordinating a smooth delivery. Please update your
            phone number here:
            <a
              class="link"
              title="Update Phone Number"
              href="https://www.yourbuzzz.com/dashboard/settings/account"
              >https://www.yourbuzzz.com/dashboard/settings/account</a
            >
          </p>

          <p>
            We understand that you are eager to receive your order, and we are
            equally excited to deliver it to you. To help us help you, please
            provide us with your phone number at the earliest convenience. This
            will not only facilitate a seamless delivery experience but also
            allow us to promptly address any queries or special instructions you
            might have regarding the delivery.
          </p>

          <p>Keep buzzing!üêù</p>

          <p>Your Best Girl, Toniaüíú</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">&copy; 2023 Buzzz. All rights reserved.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
  <style>
    * {
      font-family: 'Aeonik', sans-serif;
      line-height: 25px;
    }
    .body {
      background-color: #f1edfd;
    }
    .container {
      height: 100%;
      max-width: 1024px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 30px 15px;
    }
    .header {
      width: 100%;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .header img {
      object-fit: contain;
    }
    .contents {
      background-color: white;
      padding: 20px 20px;
      border-top: 3px solid #7047eb;
      border-bottom: 3px solid #c6b5f7;
    }
    .footer {
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      color: #6c757d;
    }
    @media (min-width: 552px) {
      .contents {
        padding: 20px 100px;
      }
      .footer {
        width: 80%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</html>
